rows.label: tlk401009_msg0001
rows.name:
The Superbian Divine Beast battleship has
extremely sturdy defenses.

rows.label: tlk401009_msg0002
rows.name:
I doubt there's a single weapon in this
whole port that could damage it.

rows.label: tlk401009_msg0003
rows.name:
Besides, I hear the main conference
will only be attended by a very select
group of trustworthy individuals.

rows.label: tlk401009_msg0004
rows.name:
I can't imagine how any miscreant
could hope to get close to the VIPs
to harm them, even if they wanted to.

rows.label: tlk401009_msg0005
rows.name:
A lot of people are on edge, but I don't
think there's anything to worry about.
